	<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">罗敖生委员：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312"> <SPAN lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">您提出的</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">关于发展昆山集成电路产业的建议</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">收悉，经研究，现答复如下：</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">一、关于加快出台产业扶持政策方面</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">根据我市半导体产业所处阶段、发展规划以及发展重点方向，经过多方调研及多轮征求意见，《昆山市半导体产业发展扶持政策意见（试行）》（见附件</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）已经昆山市政府常务会议讨论通过，并于</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2018</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>4</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>8</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">日颁布实施。前期经信委（促进中心）赴成都、合肥等地实地考察，到半导体产业发达地区取经，研究上海、南京、合肥、厦门、宁波、无锡、晋江、东莞松山湖等地半导体政策，提取总结共性做法，借鉴参考特色思路。政策旨在充分发挥昆山电子信息产业应用基础雄厚优势，加速重大龙头项目落地，强化高端人才和研发团队引进培育、提升工艺技术水平和产学研转化效率、补齐产业链关键环节薄弱短板，打造昆山半导体产业品牌特色。政策主要从培育</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>IC</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">设计、专用装备材料，产业链协同、研发支撑、金融扶持等五个方面对企业和项目精准施策。当前，我委在扶持政策的基础上，整合各科室力量，对接财政局、科技局、人社局等相关部门，正在紧锣密鼓制定政策申报指南，力争上半年出台，以进一步发挥半导体产业扶持政策可操作性强、覆盖面广、资金使用效率高的特性和效应。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">政策是产业发展的助推剂，通过政策引导精准扶持重点领域是我委面临的一项长期艰巨的任务。昆山将努力突破集成电路制造业、做强集成电路封测业、做大集成电路设备及材料等配套产业，重点打造</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>GaN</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">特色产业集聚区，大力引导芯片设计与应用结合，紧紧围绕应用市场的低成本、多品种、低功耗、快速反应等要求，加大对重点领域专用芯片的开发力度，重点发展半导体</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>IC</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">设计主要领域，包括人工智能、物联网、汽车电子、大数据等相关技术研发及产业化等。同时，支持封装企业与设计企业、制造企业间的业务整合或并购，探索新兴产业业态和创新产品，主要支持</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>Bumping</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>FlipChip</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>WL-CSP</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>TSV</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">等先进技术的研发和量产。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二、关于培育重点企业方面</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">以中科曙光、澜起科技等重大产业项目的落地为契机，发挥龙头企业对产业发展的带动作用，激发本地集成电路产业的活力，通过政策扶持鼓励企业做大做强，加快推进具有先发优势的一批重点项目建设。利用昆山当地半导体产业现有优势，在封测业、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>GaN</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">特色产业等方面错位竞争，集聚产业优势资源重点突破。注重昆山已有的封测产业基础，做好华天科技、日月光做好等本地重点企业的服务工作；大力发展化合物半导体产业，将能讯高能半导体打造成为昆山半导体产业的亮点；围绕支柱产业链条，有针对性地引进一些产业龙头项目，重点引进和培养集成电路设计业、发展专用材料和设备产业，鼓励企业做大做强，通过政策对于年度营业额达到特定规模的设计企业、半导体专用材料及设备企业进行奖励扶持。加强与企业的沟通交流，采取调研、座谈等方式，听取企业心声，尽力协调解决企业发展过程中遇到的困难。为保障半导体扶持政策实施的科学性、精准性，方便为我市半导体企业服务，中心正建立半导体领域企业数据库，企业入库采取常年受理、集中评审的方式。截止目前，已接收入库申报材料</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>90</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">份，上半年完成第一批入库认定。计划到</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2020</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年，扶持</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2-3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家集成电路封测、制造、设备、材料环节龙头企业，力争推动</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2-3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家集成电路企业实现主板上市。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三、关于创新用才机制方面</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">强化与中科院微电子所、复旦大学微电子所、西电等科研院所的深度对接合作，依托产业载体平台加速产学研项目转化落地，对接跟踪科研成果转化项目，目前已有微电子所与能讯、华天等企业开展产学研合作。在人才培养和培训方面，建立完善半导体产业高技术人才、高技能人才定制化培育体系。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年，经信、教育、人社、科技等部门联合开展全市半导体产业人才需求的调研，挖掘本地高校及人才储备资源，积极引进重点微电子院校优质教育资源在昆山设点教学。根据昆山现有的半导体产业人才短缺问题，我市已与国科大微电子学院、复旦大学微电子学院对接培训基地及定制班等相关事项，牵头组织国内外重点高校、科研院所与基地、企业共建微电子人才培养基地或中心。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">建立多层次人才支撑体系，以众创空间、产业基地、行业协会为载体，定期召集区镇分管领导、招商干部与企业相关负责人举办各类行业组织活动论坛和沙龙，邀请业内专家、企业家、职能部门</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">走进来</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">轮流上课，组织招商队伍和企业</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">走出去</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">到集成电路产业发达地区吸取先进经验做法，将原来的单向授课培训转型为政企深度对接，打造半导体人才</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">朋友圈</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">，营造半导体专业文化生态，培养出一批本土产业精英人才。为合理引导半导体产业发展，加快引进更多优质半导体项目，中心拟建立由知名专家、大学教授、企业领军人物等组成的专家库，为产业发展、项目入驻等提供意见建议、专业指导，为半导体产业发展把脉。目前，专家认定标准正在制定之中。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">针对于半导体产业人才安居问题，探索制定半导体产业人才专项政策。会同人社局等部门，做好调研，梳理现有人才相关政策；对接人才办等单位，根据我市产业发展情况，对重点产业紧缺型人才培养政策可行性进行研究；召开专题会议，听取相关单位意见和建议，结合我市实际，在我市《关于加快推进人才强市建设的若干措施》的基础上，争取在政策方面向半导体领域人才倾斜，拟定半导体产业紧缺型人才培养工程实施意见及相关政策。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">四、关于加大金融扶持力度方面</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">半导体产业投入大、周期长、见效慢，需要激发市场主体功能，利用好金融市场工具弥补昆山体量短板。通过金融扶持，解决企业融资难困境，尤其要下功夫帮助易能微等小微企业顺利渡过窗口期。对社会资本和产业资本给予一定项目运作补助，助推重大项目和核心关键环节项目更好落地。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">半导体产业的发展离不开基金的支持。下一步，我委将尽快推动昆山市半导体产业投资基金成立并确定基金管理办法，着力引进投资规模大、带动能力强、辐射范围广的重大龙头项目，以及支撑作用大、科技含量高、填补产业链空白的核心关键环节项目。鼓励兼并重组，推动重点企业产能水平提升，对接国家和江苏省相关产业投资基金，配套支持我市半导体产业项目等。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">五、关于提升公共服务软实力方面</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">进一步完善平台建设，强化载体平台建设。继续申报工信部</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">芯火</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">双创基地品牌，加强与工信部电子司、省经信委电子处对接，继续将昆山开发区作为申报主体，列入上报工信部名单，拟委托赛迪研究院在去年基础上细化完善申报材料。同时力争将昆山纳入国家集成电路产业战略，导入国家重大产业项目和国家大基金在昆山设点布局。盘活提高花桥无线测试中心、中科院微电子所等现有技术服务平台利用效率，扩宽平台服务内涵，保障开发区集成电路测试公共服务平台于</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2018</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年顺利投入使用，共享资源，为企业提供研发、测试、生产全方位服务，最终形成覆盖产业的孵化中心、设计服务平台、验证测试中心、生产测试等系列功能完善的服务体系。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">进一步加强组织保障，完善协调促进机制。加强半导体产业推进工作领导小组的统筹协调，各相关职能部门积极对上争取国家优质资源向集成电路方向倾斜，形成集全市之力、全市资源协调统一发展半导体产业的良好局面。提高协调会办能力，发挥产业促进中心牵头抓总作用，整合各方面的力量和资源，协调解决在项目推进、企业发展等过程中遇到的困难，为半导体产业发展做好保障服务工作。主动接洽产业展会、年会等，有计划地组织重点企业走出去参展参会，帮助企业对接各种展示宣传平台，营造良好产业发展环境和招商氛围。组织产业培训，提高产业内人员专业性，获取更多的产业项目信息源。今年我们将组织相关重点企业及区镇招商人员参加工信部举办的</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">名家芯思维</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">研讨会，包括化合物半导体应用发展研讨会、半导体设备产业</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2035 </SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">畅想研讨会、人工智能芯片技术和应用研讨会等。强化与芯谋研究机构招商活动的互动对接，整合篮芯会资源，金秋经贸期间，拟举办一次有影响的昆山半导体产业投资签约会；筛选昆山现有在谈项目，调研项目资金需求，利用芯谋人脉资源请芯谋策划一次项目资本对接洽谈会，为昆山半导体项目输血造势。加大力度、多角度多层次宣传昆山半导体产业发展亮点，邀请人民日报、新华日报等平面媒体来昆调研，发掘产业亮点，做</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1-2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">期专题报道；通过主流门户网站（人民网、新浪网等）、专业电子网站（赛迪网、中国半导体网）、微信公众号（半导体行业观察、</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>IC</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">咖啡）积极宣传昆山半导体产业发展及重点项目情况。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">六、下一步主要工作目标</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">我委将努力贯彻落实调研会和座谈会提出的相关要求和建议，根据提案要求，就我市半导体产业存在的问题，探索适合昆山的半导体产业的发展方向，以建设昆山市半导体产业集群为目标，将半导体产业作为昆山市推动战略性新兴产业发展和产业转型升级的战略重点，坚定不移地持续推动半导体产业的发展。以重大项目引进、龙头企业培育为突破口，加强昆山市自身半导体企业与产业链下游企业的融合发展，打造具有国内竞争力的集成电路设计业与封装测试产业为主的产业发展环境，在关键领域实现精准赶超，构建具有昆山市特色的集成电路产业发展生态体系。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">在实际工作中，我委将建立健全以下工作机制。一是协调促进机制。充分发挥市半导体产业发展领导小组统筹协调作用，协同全市各部门，对半导体产业统一领导、统筹规划，共同解决发展过程中的重大问题。各相关职能部门积极对上争取国家优质资源向集成电路方向倾斜，形成集全市之力、全市资源协调统一发展半导体产业的良好局面。建立环保研究机制，主动对接市、省、国家的环保部门，探索研究基于本地区环境保护要求的半导体项目招引方案；建立政府与企业定期对话沟通机制，通过定期调研、召开座谈会、设立政府网站专门信箱等手段，及时解决企业发展面临的实际困难，提供相关服务。二是分工落实机制。深入区镇、企业进行充分调研，结合区镇产业基础，科学制定每年度区镇任务分解目标和考核办法，督导区镇落实完成。紧盯服务项目招商核心任务，落实责任到人，集中力量、全力以赴引进一批符合我市半导体产业重点发展方向的项目和企业。三是联动发展机制。加强产业促进中心与半导体行业协会等社会主体的合作，利用协会积极对接周边协会组织，加强协会成员尤其产业链关联成员企业间深度对接。创新管理服务模式，在整合资源要素、促进产学研合作、优化市场环境、促进应用推广等方面发挥积极作用。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">通过一系列措施，计划到</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2020</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年末，全市半导体产业总产值达</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>400</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿元，年平均增长率</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>35.7%</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">（每年产值目标见表</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">）。累计新增投资项目</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>90</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个以上，引进和培育双创人才</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>100</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">人，高技能人才</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1000</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">人，产业从业人员</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2500</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">人。力争将昆山打造成为全国乃至全球有影响力的半导体细分领域特色产业集聚区。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=right><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">昆山市经济和信息化委员会</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: right; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal align=right><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2018</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US> 5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">月</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>16</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">日</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: ''Times New Roman'',''serif''; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
